Project description:
FrameFactory is the factory class  for creating  frames and surfaces.
TwoWaytisprite is a kind kind of sprite which could change its directions.
In the game, I create a sprite, a two way sprite and 5 multiple sprites.
The sprite named ghost. 
The two way sprite is a car. 
And multiple sprite are triangles.
All the sprites are draw by the gimp
You can use key T to change the target you want to track.
The background could expand and became as large as you want.

